  "detailed_description": "When terrorism threatens the world there is no need to send a bunch of iconic movie heroes back from the '80s. One under-funded over-powered mercenary is all that's needed to save the world in this epic run 'n' gun destruction-fest of a homage to Broforce!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Shoot, grenade and bludgeon</strong> your way through dozens of big and varied levels.<br></li><li>Each level is built almost entirely from <strong>destructible terrain</strong>, allowing you to carve or blast your own path however you wish.  Strategically choose a good path or gravity will punish you as you plummet to your doom!<br></li><li>Do not think you can escape the enemies by climbing ladders.<strong> They can climb them too and hunt you down!</strong><br></li><li>Engage in tough <strong>epic Boss Fights</strong> that will really test your mettle!</li></ul><br>",
  "about_the_game": "When terrorism threatens the world there is no need to send a bunch of iconic movie heroes back from the '80s. One under-funded over-powered mercenary is all that's needed to save the world in this epic run 'n' gun destruction-fest of a homage to Broforce!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Shoot, grenade and bludgeon</strong> your way through dozens of big and varied levels.<br></li><li>Each level is built almost entirely from <strong>destructible terrain</strong>, allowing you to carve or blast your own path however you wish.  Strategically choose a good path or gravity will punish you as you plummet to your doom!<br></li><li>Do not think you can escape the enemies by climbing ladders.<strong> They can climb them too and hunt you down!</strong><br></li><li>Engage in tough <strong>epic Boss Fights</strong> that will really test your mettle!</li></ul><br>",
